---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/layout/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Disclaimer — Stockade"
  description="Stockade is a trading simulator for educational purposes only. All trading uses virtual money. This is not financial advice. Read our full disclaimer."
>
  <Navbar />

  <main class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 py-16">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[#f59e0b] mb-3">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--c-text)] mb-3">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-[13px] font-mono text-[var(--c-text-subtle)]">Last updated: June 22, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Highlighted notice -->
    <div class="mb-10 rounded-xl border border-[var(--c-amber-dim)] bg-[var(--c-amber-bg)] px-6 py-5 flex gap-4">
      <svg class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-[#f59e0b]" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
        <path d="M8 1L15 14H1L8 1Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M8 6v3M8 11v.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      <p class="text-[14px] text-[#f59e0b] leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Important:</strong> Stockade is a paper-trading simulation platform. All trading is
        performed with virtual money only. Nothing on this website constitutes financial advice.
        Never invest real money based on results or strategies observed within a simulator.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-legal">

      <section>
        <h2>Simulation Only — No Real Money</h2>
        <p>
          Stockade provides a simulated trading environment using <strong>fictional price data generated
          algorithmically</strong>. All balances, profits, and losses displayed within the platform are
          entirely virtual and have no monetary value. No real stocks, cryptocurrencies, foreign
          exchange pairs, futures contracts, or any other financial instruments are bought or sold
          through this Service.
        </p>
        <p>
          Any virtual profits earned within Stockade cannot be withdrawn, converted to real currency,
          or used to purchase any goods or services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Not Financial Advice</h2>
        <p>
          The information, tools, strategies, indicators, and simulated results provided on Stockade
          are for <strong>educational and entertainment purposes only</strong>. They do not constitute
          and should not be construed as:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Financial, investment, or trading advice</li>
          <li>A recommendation to buy or sell any financial instrument</li>
          <li>Legal or tax advice</li>
          <li>An endorsement of any particular trading strategy or approach</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Always seek the advice of a qualified, licensed financial professional before making any
          real investment or trading decisions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Simulated Performance ≠ Real Results</h2>
        <p>
          Simulated or hypothetical trading results have known limitations. Unlike actual trading,
          simulated results do not account for real-world factors such as:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Market liquidity and slippage</li>
          <li>Brokerage commissions, spreads, and fees</li>
          <li>Psychological pressure of trading with real capital</li>
          <li>Execution delays, partial fills, and order rejection</li>
          <li>Real-time price discovery and market impact</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <strong>Past simulated performance is not indicative of future real-world results.</strong>
          A strategy that performs well in a simulator may perform significantly differently — or
          produce losses — when applied to live markets with real money.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Risk Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          Trading and investing in real financial markets involves <strong>substantial risk of loss</strong>,
          including the possible loss of all invested capital. Leveraged products such as futures and
          forex can amplify both gains and losses and may not be suitable for all investors.
        </p>
        <p>
          You should carefully consider your financial situation, risk tolerance, and investment
          objectives before trading real financial instruments. Stockade accepts no responsibility
          for any real financial losses incurred by users who apply strategies or techniques
          practised within the simulator to live markets.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to provide an accurate and realistic simulation experience, Stockade makes
          no representations or warranties about the accuracy, completeness, or suitability of the
          information and materials on this platform. Price data, market mechanics, and asset behaviour
          within the simulator are approximations and may differ materially from real market conditions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          This website may contain links to external sites or resources. Stockade has no control over
          the content of those sites and accepts no responsibility for them or for any loss or damage
          that may arise from your use of them.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to update this Disclaimer at any time. Changes will be reflected by
          updating the "Last updated" date above. Your continued use of the Service after any changes
          constitutes your acceptance of the revised Disclaimer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about this Disclaimer, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@stockademarketsim.com">hello@stockademarketsim.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .prose-legal section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }
  .prose-legal section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--c-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.9rem 1.4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .prose-legal li {
    list-style: disc;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #f59e0b;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .prose-legal a:hover {
    color: #fbbf24;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    color: var(--c-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
